name: Custom pumps!
description:
So you want something a little different... Pictures are some samples of other custom work we've done!

Your custom shoes will be hand-painted with fabric paints (or pens), they make an excellent gift for all and a sure way to get the envy of all those who see them! A lot of love goes into these shoes, typically taking from 4-8 hours to create to ensure a fantastic product, for you.

Note: With our current order list these may take up to 2-3 weeks to be dispatched so please allow us the time to put in the extra care for your new favourite shoes! Prices vary between sizes as for example a pair of size 10's will require hours more production time than a size 1.

Lots of love,
Def Ears

name: Pimp My Treads!
description:
Listed due to popular demand!

-PLEASE READ-
So here's the deal.

1. You send us your heels/shoes/pumps/etc of choice. Feel free to meet us if you're local to HX1 or if you're a bit further away just bubble wrap and nip them to the post office, it should cost you about £5 to post them.
2. The talented Rebecca does the artwork on them.
3. We post them back!
4. Flaunt

Done!
